getSessionAddressBooks

private OpenntfNABNamePickerData.NABDb[] getSessionAddressBooks()
                                                         throws NotesException
Compose the list of all the address books, once for ever... Beyond the cache, this guarantees that the NAB are always retrieved in the same order. The list has to be cached at the session level, as different users can have different ACLs for the databases.

Returns:
NabDb[] Array of address books
Throws:
